## 📝 معايير الكود

### TypeScript
```typescript
// ✅ صحيح
interface PrintSettings {
  pageSize: 'A4' | 'A5';
  orientation: 'portrait' | 'landscape';
}

export async function loadSettings(): Promise<PrintSettings> {
  // implementation
}

// ❌ خطأ
function loadSettings() {
  // no types, no async
}
```

### Commit Messages
```bash
feat(printing): implement DOCX template engine (phase 2)
feat(printing): add header/footer support (phase 3)
feat(printing): implement settings management (phase 4)
feat(printing): add unified generation API (phase 5)
feat(printing): add PDF conversion via LibreOffice (phase 6)
feat(printing): implement preview window (phase 7)
feat(printing): add direct printing (phase 8)
test(printing): add comprehensive test suite
docs(printing): add implementation documentation
```

---

## 🔧 المتطلبات والأدوات

### المكتبات
```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "docxtemplater": "^3.67.6",
    "pizzip": "^3.2.0",
    "libreoffice-convert": "latest"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/libreoffice-convert": "latest",
    "jest": "^30.2.0"
  }
}
```

### الأوامر الأساسية
```bash
# التثبيت
npm install libreoffice-convert

# الاختبار
npm test -- tests/printing

# الفحص
npm run lint

# التنسيق
npm run format

# البناء
npm run desktop:build

# التطوير
npm run desktop:dev
```

